in multiplayer allows, you know,
up to 16 players to take turns

00:02:04.336 --> 00:02:05.836 A:middle
and passing the turn, you know,

00:02:06.356 --> 00:02:08.856 A:middle
device in a fully
asynchronous manner.

00:02:09.656 --> 00:02:12.006 A:middle
