00:52:44.916 --> 00:52:47.326 A:middle
that you sent out
has been completed,

00:52:47.576 --> 00:52:48.836 A:middle
or any exchange has
been completed.

00:52:49.376 --> 00:52:50.116 A:middle
And this is, you know,

00:52:50.186 --> 00:52:51.556 A:middle
the player received
exchange replies.

